:{{DIcon|Talk}} I want to chat with you...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501190203: Config/Level/Mission/5011902/Act/Act501190203.json-->
::'''Boris:''' Hah hah, that's rare, someone wanting to chat with me, an artifact restorer! What would you like to talk about? I'm down for anything!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501190203_42-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501190203_42-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What does the museum do?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501190224-->
:::'''Boris:''' Well, it's a museum, so naturally, it puts up all kinds of relics and artifacts on display.
:::'''Boris:''' This museum in particular doesn't have much in its collection, and you know the reason for it &mdash; the Eternal Freeze, the Fragmentum... They took so much from us.
:::'''Boris:''' However, we still collected everything we can and restored them so that we can put them on display. Because of that, the museum is at least somewhat decent.
:::'''Boris:''' Anyway... please understand &mdash; if you feel dissatisfied during the tour &mdash; this is the best that we can do.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What does your job entail?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501190229-->
:::'''Boris:''' As an artifact restorer, my job is naturally to restore various cultural and historical pieces. Most of the artifacts and scale models that you can see in the exhibition hall were basically restored by me.
:::'''Boris:''' Speaking of which, I was once an outstanding graduate from the Belobog College of Arts back then, specializing in sculptures. Uldan hired me to help create models, and I ended up having a job here as a restorer...
:::'''Boris:''' *sigh* There are still too few professionals in Belobog.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I have no further questions.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501190233-->
:::'''Boris:''' Take care! Enjoy our exhibition.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_501190203-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I'm heading off, then.
